{
  "version": "3.1",
  "description": "gendoc 文件流水線定義 v3.1 — 唯一真相來源（Single Source of Truth）。步驟執行順序由陣列位置決定，step id 為語義識別符（無數字前綴）。新增文件類型只需在此加 step + 建立三件套 template，不需改任何 skill。",
  "condition_syntax": {
    "always": "永遠執行",
    "client_type != none": "有前台客戶端時執行（web/game）",
    "client_type == game": "遊戲類型時執行",
    "client_type != api-only": "非純 API 時執行",
    "has_admin_backend": "有 admin 後台時執行（state.has_admin_backend=true）"
  },
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "IDEA",
      "type": "IDEA",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/IDEA.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-auto",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[IDEA]"
    },
    {
      "id": "BRD",
      "type": "BRD",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/BRD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-auto",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[BRD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "PRD",
      "type": "PRD",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/PRD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[PRD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "CONSTANTS",
      "type": "CONSTANTS",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/CONSTANTS.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[CONSTANTS]",
      "note": "從 PRD 提取所有關鍵業務數值（倍率、閾值、SLO、RTP、rate-limit 等）到 docs/CONSTANTS.md（並同步輸出 docs/constants.json）。下游所有文件（EDD/BDD/test-plan/runbook）生成時必須讀取此文件並引用，確保跨文件數值一致性。這是 AI 可實作性的核心機制。"
    },
    {
      "id": "PDD",
      "type": "PDD",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/PDD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[PDD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "VDD",
      "type": "VDD",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/VDD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[VDD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "EDD",
      "type": "EDD",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/EDD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[EDD]",
      "note": "EDD 生成採用三 subagent 多 pass 架構（見 EDD.gen.md）：Pass-A 生成 §1-§8，Pass-B 生成 §4.5 UML，Pass-C 生成 §9-§21。三個 pass 均輸出到同一個 docs/EDD.md，review loop 在全部完成後執行。"
    },
    {
      "id": "ARCH",
      "type": "ARCH",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/ARCH.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[ARCH]"
    },
    {
      "id": "API",
      "type": "API",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/API.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[API]"
    },
    {
      "id": "SCHEMA",
      "type": "SCHEMA",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/SCHEMA.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[SCHEMA]"
    },
    {
      "id": "FRONTEND",
      "type": "FRONTEND",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/FRONTEND.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[FRONTEND]"
    },
    {
      "id": "AUDIO",
      "type": "AUDIO",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/AUDIO.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type == game",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[AUDIO]",
      "note": "音效設計文件：BGM/SFX/VO 清單、音效觸發邏輯、引擎設定（Cocos/Unity/HTML5 Web Audio）、資產規格、效能預算"
    },
    {
      "id": "ANIM",
      "type": "ANIM",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/ANIM.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type == game",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[ANIM]",
      "note": "動畫特效設計文件：骨骼動畫/幀動畫/Tween/粒子/Shader、引擎設定（Cocos/Unity/HTML5 PixiJS）、效能預算與 LOD 策略"
    },
    {
      "id": "CLIENT_IMPL",
      "type": "CLIENT_IMPL",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/CLIENT_IMPL.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[CLIENT_IMPL]",
      "note": "客戶端實作規格書：依 EDD §3.3 偵測引擎（Cocos Creator / Unity WebGL / React / Vue / HTML5），自動展開對應的場景結構、資源載入策略、動畫觸發規格、AudioManager 架構、VFX 整合規格。上游：EDD + VDD + ANIM + AUDIO。"
    },
    {
      "id": "ADMIN_IMPL",
      "type": "ADMIN_IMPL",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/ADMIN_IMPL.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "has_admin_backend",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[ADMIN_IMPL]",
      "note": "Admin 後台實作規格（預設技術棧：Vue3 + Element Plus + Vite）。包含：RBAC 架構、Component 規範、路由設計、API 串接、Pinia Store、部署配置。上游：EDD（§3.3 _ADMIN_FRAMEWORK, §5.5 RBAC 模型）+ ARCH + API + SCHEMA。觸發條件：has_admin_backend=true（在 gendoc-auto Session Config 中設定）。"
    },
    {
      "id": "RESOURCE",
      "type": "RESOURCE",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/RESOURCE.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[RESOURCE]",
      "note": "AI 資產生產訂單：從 VDD.md（必讀）、ANIM.md（若存在）、AUDIO.md（若存在）推導出需要哪些具體資產檔案，生成包含 ID/檔名/type/source_tool/prompt/dimensions/file_size_budget/status/output_path/description 的結構化清單。設計師確認 prompt 後即可送入 AI 工具（Midjourney/Suno/ElevenLabs 等）執行生產。觸發條件：client_type != none（有前端/客戶端的專案）。"
    },
    {
      "id": "UML",
      "type": "UML",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/diagrams/"],
      "output_glob": "docs/diagrams/*.md",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-diagrams",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[UML]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-gen-diagrams skill，生成 9 大 UML 圖 + class-inventory.md。排在所有設計文件（API/SCHEMA/FRONTEND/AUDIO/ANIM/CLIENT_IMPL/ADMIN_IMPL/RESOURCE）之後，確保所有上游文件已存在。class-inventory.md 供 test-plan 和 RTM 讀取。has_admin_backend=true 時額外生成 3 張 Admin 圖（RBAC Entity Diagram / Admin Login Sequence / Admin-Server C4 Container）。"
    },
    {
      "id": "test-plan",
      "type": "test-plan",
      "layer": "品質層",
      "output": ["docs/test-plan.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[test-plan]"
    },
    {
      "id": "BDD-server",
      "type": "BDD-server",
      "layer": "品質層",
      "output": ["features/"],
      "output_glob": "features/*.feature",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "test(gendoc)[BDD-server]",
      "note": "BDD-server.gen.md 指示生成多個 .feature 檔案 + step definitions skeleton；BDD-server.review.md 審查所有 features/*.feature（含上游 PRD/CONSTANTS 數值對照）"
    },
    {
      "id": "BDD-client",
      "type": "BDD-client",
      "layer": "品質層",
      "output": ["features/client/"],
      "output_glob": "features/client/*.feature",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "test(gendoc)[BDD-client]",
      "note": "BDD-client.gen.md 指示生成多個 .feature 檔案 + step definitions skeleton；BDD-client.review.md 審查所有 features/client/*.feature（含上游 PRD/CONSTANTS 數值對照）。has_admin_backend=true 時含 Admin RBAC BDD scenarios（login/permission/audit）。"
    },
    {
      "id": "RTM",
      "type": "RTM",
      "layer": "品質層",
      "output": ["docs/RTM.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[RTM]"
    },
    {
      "id": "runbook",
      "type": "runbook",
      "layer": "運維層",
      "output": ["docs/runbook.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[runbook]"
    },
    {
      "id": "LOCAL_DEPLOY",
      "type": "LOCAL_DEPLOY",
      "layer": "運維層",
      "output": ["docs/LOCAL_DEPLOY.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[LOCAL_DEPLOY]",
      "note": "LOCAL_DEPLOY.gen.md 要求生成後自動執行 docker/sandbox 驗證，確認所有命令可成功執行"
    },
    {
      "id": "CICD",
      "type": "CICD",
      "layer": "運維層",
      "output": ["docs/CICD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[CICD]",
      "note": "CI/CD Pipeline 設計文件。上游：EDD.md（CI_TOOL/CD_TOOL）、ARCH.md（Tech Stack）、LOCAL_DEPLOY.md（Make targets/Secret Bootstrap）。排在 LOCAL_DEPLOY 之後，確保 §4 Make targets 可從 LOCAL_DEPLOY.md §6 讀取。"
    },
    {
      "id": "DEVELOPER_GUIDE",
      "type": "DEVELOPER_GUIDE",
      "layer": "運維層",
      "output": ["docs/DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[DEVELOPER_GUIDE]",
      "note": "開發者日常操作指南（非初次建置）。上游：LOCAL_DEPLOY.md（§6 Make targets）、CICD.md（§4 Shared Make Targets、§8 Gitea）、runbook.md（incident 邊界）。排在 CICD 之後確保 CICD.md 存在可讀取。"
    },
    {
      "id": "UML-CICD",
      "type": "UML-CICD",
      "layer": "運維層",
      "output": ["docs/diagrams/"],
      "output_glob": "docs/diagrams/cicd-*.md",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-diagrams",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[UML-CICD]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-gen-diagrams skill 的 Step 2D，生成 5 張 CI/CD UML 圖（cicd-pipeline-sequence / cicd-pr-gate-activity / infra-local-topology / developer-workflow-activity / cicd-secret-flow）。排在 CICD 和 DEVELOPER_GUIDE 之後，確保 CICD.md 存在可作為 Step 2D 的上游。"
    },
    {
      "id": "ALIGN",
      "type": "ALIGN",
      "layer": "稽核層",
      "output": ["docs/ALIGN_REPORT.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-align-check",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[ALIGN]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-align-check skill，不走標準 gen→review 流程。覆蓋範圍包含 CICD.md（§4 Make targets vs LOCAL_DEPLOY.md §6）和 DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md（§2 Jenkins log path vs CICD.md §2 Jenkinsfile stage 名稱）。"
    },
    {
      "id": "ALIGN-FIX",
      "type": "ALIGN-FIX",
      "layer": "稽核層",
      "output": ["docs/ALIGN_REPORT.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-align-fix",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[ALIGN-FIX]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：依 ALIGN_REPORT.md 自動修復對齊問題（all layers），每條 fix verify 後 commit。緊接 ALIGN 執行。完成後必須觸發 ALIGN-VERIFY 重新驗證。"
    },
    {
      "id": "ALIGN-VERIFY",
      "type": "ALIGN-VERIFY",
      "layer": "稽核層",
      "output": ["docs/ALIGN_REPORT.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-align-check",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[ALIGN-VERIFY]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：ALIGN-FIX 修復完成後重新執行 gendoc-align-check，更新 ALIGN_REPORT.md 為修復後狀態，確認修復效果。若仍有 CRITICAL/HIGH 問題，繼續修復直到清零。"
    },
    {
      "id": "CONTRACTS",
      "type": "CONTRACTS",
      "layer": "實作層",
      "output": ["docs/blueprint/contracts/", "docs/blueprint/infra/", "docs/blueprint/scaffold/"],
      "output_glob": "docs/blueprint/contracts/**/*",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-contracts",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "feat(gendoc)[CONTRACTS]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：從生成文件提取機器可讀規格（OpenAPI YAML, JSON Schema, Pact, IaC, Seed Code）。輸出集中於 docs/blueprint/ 目錄。生成後自動執行 openapi-spec-validator 驗證及 path 數量對齊檢查。has_admin_backend=true 時額外輸出 admin-api.yaml + rbac-seed.json + admin-seed.json。"
    },
    {
      "id": "MOCK",
      "type": "MOCK",
      "layer": "實作層",
      "output": ["docs/blueprint/mock/"],
      "output_glob": "docs/blueprint/mock/**/*",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "client_type != api-only",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-mock",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "feat(gendoc)[MOCK]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-gen-mock skill，生成 FastAPI mock server + 擬真假資料 + frontend 使用手冊。生成後自動執行 python main.py --check 確認可啟動。整個 docs/blueprint/mock/ 目錄可獨立帶走使用。"
    },
    {
      "id": "PROTOTYPE",
      "type": "PROTOTYPE",
      "layer": "實作層",
      "output": ["docs/pages/prototype/"],
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "client_type != api-only",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-prototype",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "feat(gendoc)[PROTOTYPE]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-gen-prototype skill，依 PDD/FRONTEND/API.md 生成可點擊的 HTML prototype（UI 流程展示）+ API explorer（交互式 API 文件）。輸出至 docs/pages/prototype/，由 HTML 的 gen_html.py 自動連結到 sidebar。has_admin_backend=true 時額外生成 admin portal prototype 頁面（login/dashboard/user-list/role-management/audit-log）。"
    },
    {
      "id": "HTML",
      "type": "HTML",
      "layer": "稽核層",
      "output": ["docs/pages/"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-html",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[HTML]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-gen-html skill，不走標準 gen→review 流程。Step 1-B 開頭偵測並刪除舊版 generate_site.py（若存在），強制使用 gen_html.py。"
    }
  ]
}
